		<h1>How to make Dim sum at home</h1><br>
		<p>Traditionally, dim sum is meant to be enjoyed with a group, allowing you to sample a large number of items. But there is no reason you can't make your favorite dim sum dishes at home. Many dim sum items can be incorporated into a main meal â€“ for example, dumplings can take the place of rice or noodles. Here are my favorite dim sum recipes. </p>
